OL,3,CRobbie Williams to headline Lytham
OL,4,CFestival 2027
OL,6,FLytham Festival co-founder Peter
OL,7,FTaylor said: "What a huge start to
OL,8,F2027. Robbie Williams is music royalty
OL,9,Fand we cannot wait to welcome him to
OL,10,Four fantastic Lytham Festival next
OL,11,Fsummer.
OL,13,F"This is the first time we have
OL,14,Fannounced an artist for the following
OL,15,Fyear's festival so far in advance. The
OL,16,Fdust has barely settled on 2026 but
OL,17,Fit's such an exciting announcement
OL,18,Fthat we don't want to wait any longer
OL,19,Fthan is necessary.
OL,26,@oD@NOUuD@AOU
